snippet.title: Tesserae gameplay (PC Game, 1990)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Tesserae, Dos PC game produced by GameTek in 1990 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/tesserae/5852/
Tesserae is a very interesting puzzle/logic game. You've got to basically clear a board by jumping one different colored tile over another. A nice game created in 1990.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Chain Reaction - https://youtu.be/ak4yjVbb82U
D-Generation - https://youtu.be/A4Rp_AEzdH4
Rescue Rover 2 - https://youtu.be/Qlr5aOkXeYY
